documentation_summary: The HTML text is a PyPI (Python Package Index) project page for `types-aiobotocore-kinesisvideo` version 2.12.1, released on March 5, 2024. It provides type annotations for the `aiobotocore.KinesisVideo` service, compatible with various IDEs and tools like VSCode, PyCharm, Emacs, Sublime Text, mypy, and pyright. The annotations are generated with `mypy-boto3-builder` version 7.23.2. The package requires Python version 3.8 or higher and is licensed under the MIT License. The author of the package is Vlad Emelianov. The project aims to help in finding and fixing potential bugs by providing explicit type annotations, client annotations, paginators annotations, literals, and type definitions for better code completion and error checking in development environments.
